## Summary

CROSS-REQ-03 created the Axodus readiness and ownership alignment model using the CROSS-REQ-01 opportunity registry, CROSS-REQ-02 dependency registry and Business L4 consolidation frameworks.

The result is a portfolio-level ownership model covering 14 nuclei, 25 official opportunities and 58 official dependencies. It clarifies owners, supporters, approvers, execution owners, escalation owners, readiness states, ownership ambiguity and readiness gaps.

Assessment: READINESS_OWNERSHIP_ALIGNMENT_ESTABLISHED.

