## Execution Authority Summary

No execution authority was granted. Business remains non-executive. All execution-sensitive scopes remain owned by their nuclei and blocked until a separate future request with explicit approval.

## Recommended Resolution Sequence

1. CROSS-REQ-04 - Governance & Execution Boundary Review.
2. Resolve root global docs versioning/ownership.
3. Define treasury/financial ownership and escalation path.
4. Define Business-to-AxodusAPP read-only consumer contract.
5. Review ACS, Trading, Marketplace, Mining, Lottery and Dex execution-sensitive gates before implementation cycles.

